设施：可以', '["https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233y12000b0zzrm89A8C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232y12000b0ztesgED79_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232t12000b10bue13F12_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236412000b10iqn11748_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233312000b10gtcp2AB7_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231t12000b10pe476462_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235112000b102mm2355B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231s12000b10btz9A293_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232812000b10nbbxD626_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg"]'::jsonb, 5, 5, '2023-04-22', '花园双床房', '双床房', '朋友出游', 23, 0, 20, 3, '["整体满意度","卫生状况"]'::jsonb, '整体满意度', '卫生状况', NULL),
('680280d2e3c98b0941765e14', '一整个非常满意！！', '["https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233q12000bbvf83j5E2E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231a12000bbv82ix6942_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233312000bbv98kk727A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232k12000bbvcy1oE5D9_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235i12000bbvf83n7F85_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234r12000bbvc99p477E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg"]'::jsonb, 5, 5, '2023-05-31', '花园双床房', '双床房', '朋友出游', 9, 0, 14, 2, '["整体满意度"]'::jsonb, '整体满意度', NULL, NULL),
('680280d2e3c98b0941765e15', '老酒店一直保养的挺好，服务也很好，前台帅哥给房间做了升级，还送了早茶和下午茶，早上吃过早茶后花园观光一下心情舒畅，以后再来广州一定来住花园酒店，来酒店花园赏鱼，真的舒服', '["https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0203o12000aeke6wa0599_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0203r12000aekd56fF587_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0203u12000aeke3lvB77F_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg"]'::jsonb, 5, 5, '2023-01-08', '花园大床房', '大床房', '情侣出游', 84, 0, 41, 8, '["整体满意度","前台服务","餐饮设施"]'::jsonb, '整体满意度', '前台服务', '餐饮设施')
